Feature: Navigation partial scenarios

  Scenario: I execute first partial
    Given I am on the homepage
    Then  I should be on the homepage
    And I should be on "/"
    And the url should match ^\/

  Scenario: I execute second partial
    Given I am on the homepage
    And   I reload the page
    Then  I should be on the homepage

  Scenario: I execute third partial
    Given I am on the homepage
    And   I follow "h2.post-title a"
    Then  I wait 1 second
    Then  I should be on "/post/1"
    And the url should match ^\/post\/\d+
    Then  I move backward one page
    Then  I should be on the homepage

  Scenario: I execute fourth partial
    Given I am on "/post/2"
    Then  I should be on "/post/2"
